          "source": "Where skill output lands. Individual skills can override this via their SKILL.md output: field. Inline streams into the current note at cursor. New note creates a separate file in the same folder.",
          "target": "技能输出的去处。各个技能可以通过其 SKILL.md 的 output: 字段覆盖此设置。内联会将输出流式插入当前笔记的光标处。新建笔记会在同一文件夹中创建一个单独的文件。"
