          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When ON, agent skills (mode: agent) can call write_note and append_note to create or overwrite notes. When OFF (default), those tools return an error and the agent reports back without writing. Recommended OFF — a prompt-injected agent should not silently modify your vault.",
